    "body": "This PR removes a check in arg_utils.py for FP8 that is not necessary.  It turns out that a different backend is used for FP8 when running FP8 on V1 so it will not hit the Triton backend, even if VLLM_USE_TRITON_FLASH_ATTENTION=1 is set.\n",
